user.biography:
Curated kook slammage. 
Submit your videos for a chance to be immortalized on our page forever.
Slam our seltzer @KookslamsHardSeltzer

node.text:
@kookslamshardseltzer NEW STORE LOCATIONS UPDATE!

Attention San Diego and Orange County. We have an updated list of stores to pickup our hard seltzy. Find the one near you and clear those suckers ouuuut!!

𝗡𝗲𝘄𝗽𝗼𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗲𝗮𝗰𝗵
Henry’s Groceries
Dory Deli

𝗣𝗮𝗰𝗶𝗳𝗶𝗰 𝗕𝗲𝗮𝗰𝗵
Iron Pig
Palm Liquor
Bare Back Grill
Amplified Ale Works
The Open Bar

𝗟𝗶𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁𝘆 𝗦𝘁𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻
Moniker Coffee

𝗢𝗰𝗲𝗮𝗻 𝗕𝗲𝗮𝗰𝗵
OB Kabob

Go pick up some of our glory nectar and tag @kookslamshardseltzer so we can proclaim your name on the Mt.Rushmore of stoke.

You can also order online for CA delivery if none of these stores are close to you. Link in bio.

node.text: “Who’s your favorite surfer?” …. “You’ve never heard of him.” #becomeungovernable #rastastormSUPlegend #costcoteamrider via @dingosaidso @surfinggoats

@kookslamshardseltzer IS LIVE! Order now at the link in our bio!! All orders will begin shipping on 6/24.
We have been working on this product and brand for the last year and are ridiculously pumped to finally be sending it. This is not a collab, this is not a co-brewing experiment, this is a Kookslams startup my dudes. So if we've ever made you laugh or most likely just blow a little air out your nose when you slightly laugh at something on the interwebs, we would greatly appreciate the support, because we literally have a brewery we need to keep the lights on at now. Our first run of cannage is limited so you should pull the trigger before we sell out.
